about_des.des:
Welcome to AM Rubber Industries, a leading manufacturer of high-quality rubber products. Established in 1989, we have been providing our customers with exceptional products and services for over 34 years.
Our state-of-the-art manufacturing facility is located in Kottayam, equipped with the latest technology and machinery to ensure efficient and precise production of rubber products. We have a dedicated team of skilled professionals who are committed to delivering products that meet the highest standards of quality and safety.
At AM Rubber Industries, we offer a wide range of rubber products to meet the diverse needs of our customers. Our product portfolio includes O-rings, Oil and Water Seals, Gaskets, Car Mats, Scooter Mats, Mat Connectors, Mudflaps, Bushes, Metal Bounded Rubber Products and many other custom tailored rubber products. We use only the finest materials to ensure the durability and longevity of our products.
We take pride in our commitment to environmental sustainability and responsible manufacturing practices. We use eco-friendly materials and processes to reduce our carbon footprint and promote a healthier planet.
At AM Rubber Industries, our mission is to exceed our customers' expectations by providing them with the best products and services. We believe in building long-term relationships with our customers based on trust and mutual respect.
Thank you for considering AM Rubber Industries for your rubber product needs. We look forward to serving you!
